name: BayAreaTransit
0:
”Alexa, open Bay Area transit”
”When is the next caltrain”
”When is the Caltrain after 8AM going from Redwood City to San Francisco”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: bay area transit
des: This app allows users to find out when the next Caltrain is to a certain station. It also can let users know which Caltrain reaches the fastest to a certain location. We are continuing to add to this application and will soon be adding special schedules such as Giants days, sharks days and fireworks days. This is app is not affiliated with the official Caltrain organization in any way.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
